title: Ranakshetra
subTitle: When Santu protests against availability of drugs and gets murdered by a minister's son, his brother, Raja decides to seek justice on his own after his legal efforts go in vain.

title: Gate 2 Gether
subTitle: Rick dislikes Diya initially but falls in love with her when he realises that she is his childhood friend. However, Diya is in a dilemma as she is already committed to her boyfriend.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Lord Shiva loses his temper when Kambasura comes to take Parvati with him, and Parvati accepts Narada's advice to win Lord Shiva's heart.

title: Meghe Dhaka Tara
subTitle: Neeta is the beautiful daughter of a middle-class refugee from East Pakistan. She sacrifices everything for her family while they exploit her goodness and take advantage of her.

title: Naga Panchami
subTitle: A man kills his sister and throws her family into disarray. However, his sister's daughter, a shape-shifting snake, is determined to seek revenge.

title: Sathi Amar
subTitle: After his parents' death, Raja takes care of his sister and falls in love with one of her friends, Jyoti. He attempts his best to win over his lover.

title: I Love You
subTitle: Puja is brought up by her brother Indra at a farm. She falls in love with Rahul, a rich boy, but his family insults her rustic upbringing. In order to win her back, Rahul starts working for Indra.

title: Paribar
subTitle: Rahul ventures into the smuggling business and lands in trouble. However, his brother Sagar takes the blame to protect him and their family.

title: Baro Bou
subTitle: Tapan and his wife generously provide for their joint family. However, when the younger brother marries his employer's daughter, he becomes arrogant, which creates a rift within the family.

title: Amanush
subTitle: Vinod, an orphan, finds his soul mate in Rhea, who cares a lot for him but loves Aditya. Dejected and irate, Vinod becomes a psychopath killer to win her over.

title: Amanush
subTitle: Vinod, an orphan, finds his soul mate in Rhea, who cares a lot for him but loves Aditya. Dejected and irate, Vinod becomes a psychopath killer to win her over.

title: Antarleen
subTitle: Aniket Sanyal, a detective, is forced to resume work during his much-needed, long vacation after a mysterious death of a tourist.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: As Parvati attempts to make a Shivling, Lord Shiva destroys it and seeks to prevent her from doing it. However, she refuses to give up and continues to battle the challenges he throws her. Will she succeed?

title: Arshinagar
subTitle: Ranajit and Julekha belong to rival families who have been enemies for years. However, when they meet, there is an unbeatable connection that eventually turns into love.

title: Gariber Samman
subTitle: Being the eldest daughter, Madhavi takes up the responsibility of uniting the family during hard times. She sacrifices her love and happiness to protect the honour of the family.

title: Dada Thakur
subTitle: Gita plans to reunite with her long-estranged father, not knowing that he is waiting for her younger sister, Mita, to return. The two siblings then struggle to win back his trust.

title: Amader Sansar
subTitle: Soumen goes against his mother's will and decides to tie the knot with his teacher's daughter in order to make him happy.

title: Greftaar
subTitle: Arun Roy, a police sub-inspector, comes face-to-face with a corrupt political leader, Indrajit, and stands up to him. As a result, his father is humiliated and suspended from the police.

title: Sangee
subTitle: When Bijay comes to Calcutta for higher studies, he meets Rupa and instantly falls in love with her. However, he is unaware that she is his friend Rana's sister.

title: Bikram Singha: The Lion Is Back
subTitle: Gupi, an imposter, finds a gang of thugs pursuing him after a six-year-old girl believes him to be her father. Later, he learns a shocking secret about the girl's life.

title: Bikram Singha: The Lion Is Back
subTitle: Gupi, an imposter, finds a gang of thugs pursuing him after a six-year-old girl believes him to be her father. Later, he learns a shocking secret about the girl's life.

title: Durga Sohay
subTitle: A mother-daughter relationship develops between Manasi, the younger daughter-in-law of an aristocratic family, and Durga, a maid, when she gives her a second chance after the house-help is caught stealing.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Making Parvati's path more difficult, Lord Shiva disguises himself as a saint and distracts her. However, Parvati is determined to complete her purpose.

title: Mishor Rohosyo
subTitle: Al Mamun, an Egyptian business tycoon, asks his friend Kakababu to help him decode some hieroglyphic symbols that will help trace the will of his teacher, Mufti Mohammad.

title: Toofan
subTitle: Shanto, an aspiring actor, is forced to be a body-double for Toofan, a mafia kingpin. Unexpected twists, turns and chaos follow.

title: Sejo Bou
subTitle: A poor man falls in love with a girl belonging to a wealthy family. In an attempt to separate them, the man is sent abroad. However, the couple's destiny intervenes, striving to bring them together.

title: Bhalobasa Bhalobasa
subTitle: Sidhu meets and falls in love with a woman named Priya despite being engaged to a different girl. He soon has to make a choice between following his heart and respecting his father's wishes.

title: Mon Mane Na
subTitle: On their way to Siliguri, India, Rahul and Ria bump into each other. While Rahul plans to sell a stolen necklace, Ria is excited to meet her boyfriend.

title: Poran Jaye Jolia Re
subTitle: A young man, Rabin, meets three different women at different stages in his life. The relationship he shares with these women, though very different from each other, help him grow as a person.

title: Bojhena Shey Bojhena
subTitle: A tragic love story intertwines the lives of four strangers, leading to unexpected bonds and heartbreak, forever altering their paths after a devastating accident.
